  <title>Modules</title>

  <indexterm>
    <primary>modules</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <para>
    With the default preset, modules are organized into three functional groups: technical, grading and effects.
    You either view all modules in one long list or instead click on a group to just
    display modules belonging to that group.
  </para>

